{"id":7866,"date":"2024-01-16T18:05:33","date_gmt":"2020-04-16T12:35:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7866"},"modified":"2023-10-23T18:15:13","modified_gmt":"2023-10-23T12:45:13","slug":"window-seat-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/window-seat-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Transform Your Window Space With These Amazing Window Seat Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>A window seat helps you enjoy the beauty of nature\/cityscape apart from giving you a place to relax comfortably. It is indeed a timeless feature that transcends short-lived trends.&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Though window seats are only a simple and minimalist design element, they can add great value to your home with the perfect combination of practicality and aesthetics. Window seats can be incorporated either into your living room, dining room and most often, your bedrooms. They bring light into the space, provide extra seating for your special guests and close family, and is also a place for self-reflection.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s have a look at these amazing window seat ideas that are a perfect blend between comfort and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Cozy Reading Nook<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This comfy upholstered window seat designed into the corner of this grey room with a white baseboard is minimalistic. The set of drawers below allow for some extra storage of smaller items while tall windows above open up this small room and make it look more welcoming and bright. The floor-to-ceiling multi-level&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/bookshelf-design-for-home\/\">home bookshelf<\/a>&nbsp;serves as a boon to all those avid readers who find it difficult to organise their bookcases.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174259\/cozy-window-seat-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Corner window seat ideas add a bookshelf and set of drawers for some extra storage.\" class=\"wp-image-7871\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174259\/cozy-window-seat-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174259\/cozy-window-seat-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174259\/cozy-window-seat-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174259\/cozy-window-seat-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black And Brown Window Seat For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This white-themed room with a dark accent wall is balanced well by an intelligently-built niche window seat area that resembles a modern looking bench. Throw in some brown and grey coloured cushions over the beige seat cushion and similar-themed short curtains to make this spot extra cozy while you view the breathtaking landscape outside. Alternatively, you can take a quick nap here when you tire of working.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174615\/window-seat-colour-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Window side seating colour ideas with white-themed room with a dark accent wall.\" class=\"wp-image-7875\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174615\/window-seat-colour-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174615\/window-seat-colour-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174615\/window-seat-colour-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174615\/window-seat-colour-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Compact And Cute Window Seat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This window seat, enclosed between a shelf and bed in the corner of a blue and white themed kid\u2019s room, is a private space that\u2019s meant for just one. This window seating design gives your kid some \u2018me time\u2019. It comes with a pair of open cabinets below for additional storage and helps you utilise a corner that would have most probably been overlooked and wasted. The simplistic design makes this space look orderly and uncluttered.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174218\/compact-bedroom-window-seat-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom window seat ideas can opt for open cabinets below for additional storage and helps you utilise a corner.\" class=\"wp-image-7870\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174218\/compact-bedroom-window-seat-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174218\/compact-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174218\/compact-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174218\/compact-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Explore multifunctional home interiors for your seating space\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/23173822\/explore-multifunctional-home-interiors-for-your-seating-space.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/kids-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">Kids Bedroom Design Ideas For Your Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Elongated Window Side Seat With Curtain<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add more functionality to a window seat by incorporating it into the dining room. The wall-to-wall elongated window seat harmoniously blends into the room\u2019s landscape, runs along the windowpane and provides extra seating area for family members and occasional guests. It looks attractive and complements the classic&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/dining-room-design\/\">dining room interior<\/a>&nbsp;with a medium-tone hardwood floor, grey walls, a glass-door, built-in cabinets and elegant dining room furniture.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174352\/elongated-window-side-seating-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Elongated window seat ideas add extra seating for family members and occasional guests that look airy.\" class=\"wp-image-7872\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174352\/elongated-window-side-seating-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174352\/elongated-window-side-seating-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174352\/elongated-window-side-seating-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174352\/elongated-window-side-seating-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For The Blue Lovers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a modern window seat incorporated in a sea-inspired&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/blue-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">blue bedroom<\/a>. The upholstery of the window seat matches perfectly with other elements in the room such as the design of throw pillows, pair of chairs at home study\/office desk and the valance. The charm of a comfortable window seat makes it seem a part of the overall feel and design of the room. A light colour palette offers for a peaceful place to relax.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174841\/window-side-seating-ideas-blue-lovers.jpg\" alt=\"Window side seating ideas arrange study\/office desk for a peaceful to work\/study\" class=\"wp-image-7878\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174841\/window-side-seating-ideas-blue-lovers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174841\/window-side-seating-ideas-blue-lovers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174841\/window-side-seating-ideas-blue-lovers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174841\/window-side-seating-ideas-blue-lovers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Nature-Inspired Window Seating For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This nature-inspired window seating creates a beautiful&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interior<\/a>. The white, light brown and green-themed colour palette, coupled with animal motifs on the throw cushions, effectively bring in nature\u2019s vibes and creates a calming atmosphere. It makes the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">small bedroom interiors<\/a>&nbsp;look airy too.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174527\/nature-inspired-bedroom-window-seat-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Window seat ideas nature-inspired window seating creates a beautiful bedroom interior\" class=\"wp-image-7874\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174527\/nature-inspired-bedroom-window-seat-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174527\/nature-inspired-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174527\/nature-inspired-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174527\/nature-inspired-bedroom-window-seat-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Calming Hues<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Take maximum advantage of a white-themed&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room interior<\/a>&nbsp;that is luminous by adding a portable window seat to the existing armchair and sofa combo. All the muted colours of the furniture and upholstery mix and match harmoniously with each other. Use the window seat comfortably as a reading area in a corner that separates you from the busier areas of the house.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174748\/window-seat-ideas-living-room-calming-hues.jpg\" alt=\"Window seat ideas make comfortably as a reading area in a corner with mix and match colours of furniture.\" class=\"wp-image-7877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174748\/window-seat-ideas-living-room-calming-hues.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174748\/window-seat-ideas-living-room-calming-hues-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174748\/window-seat-ideas-living-room-calming-hues-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174748\/window-seat-ideas-living-room-calming-hues-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Girly Twist<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a girly twist to your little one\u2019s bedroom by transforming the corner window area to a pleasant lounging space that is well-lit, and which can double up as a reading or quick napping nook. All the layers and texture of the pink and purple textured floral pillows as well as turquoise animated accent wall, fills the entire area with warmth and coziness.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moving on, you can keep a few quick tips in mind when you plan to designing your window seat arrangements so you don\u2019t compromise on pleasure or functionality that it\u2019s going to provide you:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Cushions \u2013 Cushions make window seats much more comfortable to sit on. Carefully choose the right kind and quality of foam you will make your cushions from. The most common window seat cushions used are the rectangular-shaped box cushions that easily fit over the top of your window seat and are adjustable<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Space-saving storage options \u2013 Building in additional storage under your window seat is a great idea and it can be done in many different ways. You can design your window seat with either a hinged lift-up top that opens vertically or pull-out cupboards\/ drawers&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Size \u2013 The size of the window seat will depend upon the purpose you are going to use it for. For example, if you are planning to stretch out on the sofa and lounge around all day reading books or snoozing, then your window seat will need to be long and deep enough to accommodate you properly<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174440\/girly-twist-window-seat-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom window seat ideas double up as a reading or quick napping nook that feels warmth and cosiness.\" class=\"wp-image-7873\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174440\/girly-twist-window-seat-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174440\/girly-twist-window-seat-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174440\/girly-twist-window-seat-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/16174440\/girly-twist-window-seat-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope that this blog has inspired you to design or spruce up your very own comfy corner. So, what are you waiting for? Get the ball rolling now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/window-decoration-ideas\/\">Window Decoration Ideas For Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/seating-ideas-for-home\/\">Seating Ideas For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/teenage-girls-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">Teenage Girls Bedroom Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/